UNITED STATES of America v. Bennie Lee BERRY et al. Bennie Lee BERRY et al. v. Martha LONG et al. Nos. 3632, 3633. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Jan. 20, 1948. Cleon A. Summers, U. S. Atty., of Muskogee, Okl., for the United States. Turner & Turner, of Holdenville, Okl., A. W. Trice, of Ada, Okl., and W. M. Haulsee, of Wewoka, Okl., for Bennie Lee Berry et al.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.
